title: Update Brand Logo
body:
Some members of the Web3API DAO have mentioned that the bio-organisms inside the current logo are confusing and complicated things a bit. Also, one of the organisms looked like the coronavirus, so we've been needing to change our logo for a while.

I'd like to propose we start using the simpler version of the logo I submitted  for April's mini-hack (which can be seen here: https://github.com/Web3-API/mini-hacks/issues/3) as the official logo for our brand
author: 0x37341cbb14c5F128A70B149726ad8B2CE6F4C793
